The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) tasks, specifically in the medical domain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also evaluates the performance of different representation methods, which could fall under categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
